## Interface: 110002
## Title: WinUILib
## Notes: WinUI-inspired, token-driven UI framework for World of Warcraft addon developers.
## Version: 1.0.0
## Author: Weischbier
## X-Category: Library
## X-License: MIT
## DefaultState: enabled
## LoadOnDemand: 0

# ── Core runtime ──────────────────────────────────────────────
Core/Bootstrap.lua
Core/Utils.lua
Core/EventBus.lua
Core/StateMachine.lua
Core/FramePool.lua

# ── Token / theme system ─────────────────────────────────────
Tokens/Registry.lua
Tokens/DefaultTheme.lua

